@alienatix I was wondering if we set `recurse` to false and if only the parent is meant to be deleted and not the children, what will take the place of the parent?

Or should we keep it similar to GUI where you right click a node and if you delete all its subnodes are deleted without having the choice of just deleting the parent.

Would really like your views on this @kingthorin , @psiinon , @thc202.
